nfirmDelete,\n\t\tcloseDeleteModal,\n\t};\n}\n","message":"Wrote contents to /Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/pageComponents/users/hooks/useUserLibraryPage.ts"}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-52072bef-d9df-4bd1-865e-d69187c21bfc-49\nfc_ca053991-3481-99ff-b6a2-93f350d99343_0","startedAtMs":"1784806298275","completedAtMs":"1784806298789"},"model_call_id":"a25a74f1-b71b-4206-ac8b-ed45eaa7e341-8-mawn","session_id":"9889126d-666f-4037-9a22-48d049bc9da4","timestamp_ms":1784806298776}
